  "producer_obligations": [
    "Stage6 must project the unified fact hub as the only authoritative source for Stage7 commercial seed fields.",
    "Stage6 must carry formal producer object ids for project_fact, review_queue_profile, report_record, and challenger_candidate_profile so Stage7 can bind sales objects back to Stage6 carriers.",
    "Stage6 must carry review/report state and any isolated supplement references as machine-readable metadata without leaking supplement content into Stage7 formal objects.",
