    "Stage6 must not downgrade H-05 gate authority into free-form Stage7 defaults."
  ],
  "consumer_obligations": [
    "Stage7 must consume H-06 required/minimum producer fields as authoritative inputs for producer object ids, sale_gate_status, saleability_status, competitor_quality_grade, window_status, report_status, review_task_status, review_lane, action_family, challenger profile seeds, and actor/buyer seeds.",
    "Stage7 must not recompute Stage6 unified fact decisions from Stage5 gate inputs, review_queue internals, or governed supplement content.",
    "Stage7 sales_lead, buyer_fit, offer_recommendation, and saleable_opportunity must be constrained when H-06 carries linked_review_request_id_optional or missing_condition_family_optional.",
